parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.I’m too scared to fire the receptionist at Channel 4. But she leaves junk everywhere!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Box up 4 bags of junk that she’s left inside the Channel 4 building, tell her to leave and I’ll give you a reward.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.The receptionist jumped out of the window.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Thanks for doing my dirty work. What would you like as a reward?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She left the building just moments ago.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.I’m Detective Canmore. I’m here for the interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeFrEx.Ah, yes. Detective. The commissioner arrived moments ago.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeBaEx.The segment will be taping soon. Come with me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeBaEx.Miss Foxx is not yet ready to see you. Come back later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeBaEx.Miss Foxx is not yet ready to see you. Come back later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeBaEx.Miss Foxx is waiting for you upstairs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeAnEx>.If you don’t have an appointment I can’t just let you up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I need to speak to him now!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Miss Kimura. I’m sorry I didn’t come to you earlier, but…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.We’re going to clear this up with Paul and then there will be absolutely no one else allowed near that mansion apart from those I authorize.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Are we going to bring in more security? Lillian’s not going to like that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.That won't be necessary. I have a different plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe>.Are you kidding me? Interfering with our efforts to find the thieves responsible for breaking into the Wilkes mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx>.What exactly do you expect to find? If you want to know something about the mansion, come to us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnDe.No offense, Commissioner, but you know as well as I do that’s not how it works.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp>.I’ve cooperated with your organization. Do you not trust me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnDe.What the hell did you do, Paul?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.He was caught snooping around the mansion at night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx>.There are officers posted there, looking for thieves. You could have been shot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnDe.They are looking for thieves? In Wilkes’ back yard?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp>.Are you suggesting we’re hiding something from you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnEx.Miss Kimura has been nothing but helpful to us in the past.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnDe.The public has a right to know what’s happening. The Guild operates here in North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe>.Is that what you want to hear? That the thieves are connected to the Eclipse Guild?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe>.You run a news segment on Sunday.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx>.Meet Canmore and I here tonight. We’ll give you everything we know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx>.In return, you stay the hell away from the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.Of course. If Miss Kimura is willing to work with us, I see no reason to interfere with her investigation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaEx.We can film the slot tonight at seven.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Right now? She won’t be at work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Organize everything you have and meet me at my home in four hours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.Great. Melissa is going to be really happy to see me on Saturday.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl^.I hope her office number forwards to her cell phone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe^.I could visit her at her home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.This day is just getting better and better.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.1Hero, I don’t know what to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Just stay here. I’ll get your uniform back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.1Hero, I don’t know what to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Just stay here. I’ll get your uniform back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx.I haven’t been able to get anywhere with security.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeAnOp>.Detective Canmore, is this man with you? What’s going on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.She’s… very troubled right now. I think she’ll be here soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.And when she gets here, she’s going to try broadcasting something crazy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Paul, this is very important: She can’t be allowed to broadcast that message. No matter what.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnDe^.Yeah, I know. If we let her go on-air like that, we’d lose our audience.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s more. She has people helping her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Dangerous people, Paul. You need to be careful.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlShCl^.This doesn’t make any sense. Who are you people?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.They’re friends of mine, here to help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeBaEx^.What about the police? Where are they?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlBaDe^.Yeah, 1Hero, does Commissioner Kimura know what’s going on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.The commissioner is… indisposed. She can’t assist us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll see about getting help from the police station. In the meantime, my friends will help you in case anything happens.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Don’t worry, the Lord is with us. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlWoDe^.1Hero… why is there a priest here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.When things get hairy, we’ll need him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlShDe^.Monsters and priests? This has to be some kind of joke.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I wish it were... I should go to the studio. If the worst should happen and they make it there, that’s where I need to be.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Paul, Father Solomon is right. If something happens, you should listen to him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlWoOp^.As long as nothing goes on air, I’ll trust you... for now. But I’d really like to know what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Explanations will have to wait. Right now, we have to act fast. They could show up at any moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeWoOp^.I don’t understand what’s going on. If there’s danger, police should be here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SeBaEx^.I’ll clear the public areas… After that, I’ll head over to the security room to watch the cameras for anything suspicious.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaOp.I’ll scope out the perimeter. The earlier we see them coming, the better.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Let’s just hope they use the front door.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.1Hero… How sure are you Judy is safe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Fairly confident… But I’ll check on her when I get to the police station.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnDe^.But if Kimberly’s new weirdo bodyguards are on the way, I guess I’d better get to locking down the building, and make sure the studio is secure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.I don’t really look forward to being surrounded by police.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.For now, let’s just focus on stopping the apocalypse.");
